--- ViewHomelabError
div w-full h-full flex-col bg-[#aa0000] text-[#aa0005]
  if {viewport_width < 80 || viewport_height < 24}
    include views.crepus#ViewMinimumSize viewport_width={viewport_width} viewport_height={viewport_height}
  else
    if {viewport_width >= 120}
      div w-full h-full flex-row
        div w-[120] h-full
