--- ViewMinimumSize
div w-full h-full flex-col bg-[#aa0000] text-[#aa0005] justify-center items-center
  div h-[1] text-[#aa0009] "Terminal too small"
  div h-[1] text-[#aa0008] "requires 80×24, current {viewport_width}×{viewport_height}"
